## Workflow checklist

- [ ] `rd_plan.md` states the current R&D category.
- [ ] Current-state assessment names the blocking uncertainty.
- [ ] Planned work has a plan section or pre-registration before
  claim-bearing execution.
- [ ] Execution results are compared against the plan.
- [ ] Evidence artifacts are linked from `rd_plan.md` or `decisions.md` when
  decision-relevant.
- [ ] Claim-bearing or preregistered results have a readable report package
  with visual or tabular evidence.
- [ ] Report provenance exists for claim-bearing or preregistered report
  packages when produced.

